Group Chat

METHOD TO ALLOW ONLY ONE PERSON TO DRAW AT A TIME

- Client side does the action. draw, erase, reset
- Sever side ONLY handles data! Flag to notify users that someone is drawing


The info the server has
1. users = [] ====> an array of users. Updated when people sign on or off


2. user_info = []  ====> info of users 
	a. user_id
	b. name
	c. room 

3. drawer = user_id ===> shows who is taking the drawing

3. chats = []

4. canvas_free => set to true or false based on user click


